          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/u/lescape">@LeScape</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>Declare:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">public int shoutDelay;</code></pre>
<p>Then add this command:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">if (command.startsWith("shout")) {
if (shoutDelay &lt;= 0) {
String messageToSend = command.substring(6);
shoutDelay = 60;
PlayerHandler.messageToAll = playerName+" shouts: "+messageToSend;
} else if (shoutDelay &gt;= 1) {
sendMessage("You must wait before shouting again.");
}
}</code></pre>
<p>All hand written. <img src="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/images/emoji/twitter/wink.png?v=6" title=":wink:" class="emoji" alt=":wink:"></p>
